{"id":4778,"title":"Care of patients with Ebola virus disease.","abstract":"Caring for patients with Ebola virus disease requires strict biosafety protocols to eliminate exposure and ensure containment. Training and competency verification were critical to creation of a safe environment for nursing staff involved in the direct care of two patients with Ebola virus disease at Emory University Hospital.","date":"2014-11-04","categories":"Virus Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25365183","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.384226,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Nursing","weight":0.259122,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nursing"},{"name":"Natural environment","weight":0.247671,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_environment"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.236941,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Ebola","weight":0.221135,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ebola"},{"name":"Emory University","weight":0.202673,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emory_University"},{"name":"Nurse","weight":0.152786,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse"},{"name":"Virus","weight":0.0494293,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virus"},{"name":"Biosafety","weight":0.0329831,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biosafety"},{"name":"Containment","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Containment"},{"name":"Teaching hospital","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teaching_hospital"},{"name":"Medical guideline","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_guideline"},{"name":"Hypothermia","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypothermia"},{"name":"Skill","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skill"},{"name":"Viral disease